title: Louif Skate Day
description: I shot this skateboarding with the intent of using it for a Day in the Life with Louif when I was staying with him in Quebec back in October. Unfortunately the audio was either messed up or nonexistent on all of my interview clips. But the skating was fun and fine. So here it is with some clips of Will Lavigne and my new homie Marco!
